{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "大老板与军师竹叶青商讨如何对付\"没有用的阿吉\"。竹叶青分析阿吉轻易废掉崆峒高手铁拳阿勇，判断其武功深不可测，并已派出大量人手调查阿吉来历却一无所获。竹叶青提出以\"拖\"字诀消耗阿吉一方的体力和精神，同时在阿吉住处布下眼线监视苗人兄妹。阿吉识破竹叶青派来的男扮女装探子，逼问出铁头大刚的下落和铁虎的信息，决定主动出击而非坐以待毙。阿吉与苗家兄妹分食最后的食物，娃娃含泪劝阻阿吉不要冒险，阿吉仍毅然前往铁头大刚三姨太的赌馆，揭露其至尊宝牌局并以冷言震慑全场。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等到阳澄湖的那批大螃蟹送来，说不定也就恰巧是这些菊花开得最好的时候。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那真是好极了，好极了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们说那个人叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁拳阿勇",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他叫阿吉，没有用的阿吉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿吉？没有用的阿吉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "他叫没有用的阿吉，你叫铁拳阿勇？",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁拳阿勇",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "是你的拳头硬，还是他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁拳阿勇",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是他的拳头硬。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "是你勇敢？还是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁拳阿勇",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "是你没有用？还是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁拳阿勇",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "这么看来，好像是你的名字叫错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁拳阿勇",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "那么你为什么不改个名字，叫废物阿狗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他已经尽了力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫他滚吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "再弄点银子叫他养伤去，伤好了再来见我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_quan_a_yong",
      "text": "大老板叫你到账房去领一千两银子，你还不谢恩。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "一出手就是一千两，你这人倒是大方得很。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "只可惜我这也是慷他人之慨。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "你这个人最大的好处，就是会说老实话。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我还有几句老实话要说。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "退下去。",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "那个没有用的阿吉，绝不是没有用的人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "铁拳阿勇是崆峒出身的，近年来崆峒虽然已人才凋零，可是他们的独门功夫仍然有它的独到之处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "崆峒不坏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "在崆峒弟子中，阿勇一直是最硬的一把手，还没有被逐出门墙时，就已经干掉过少林的四个大和尚，武当的两把剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "这些事我都知道，否则我怎么会花八百两银子一个月用他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "可是那个没有用的阿吉，却一下子就把他废了，由此可见，阿吉这个人很不简单。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "奇怪的是这附近方圆几百里之内，竟没有一个人知道他的来历。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "你调查过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我已经派出了六十三个人，都是地面上耳目最灵通的，现在回来的已经有三十一个人，都没有查出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "你究竟想说什么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "这个人留在附近，迟早总是个祸害。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "那么你就赶快叫人去做了他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "叫谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "铁头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "大刚'油头贯顶'的功夫，的确已很少有人能比得上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "我亲眼看过他一头撞断一棵树。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "只可惜阿吉不是树。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "他的硬功夫也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "比阿勇的铁拳功也强不了太多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "你认为他也对付不了那个没有用的阿吉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "不是绝对不行，只不过没有把握而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我记得大老板曾经吩咐过，没有把握的事，绝对不能做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我想来想去，我们这边有把握能对付他的人，只有一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "铁虎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "大老板当然也知道他的来历，这个人机智深沉，平时出手，从不肯露出他真功夫来，却已经比大刚、阿勇高出很多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "他要到什么时候才能回来？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他这次差事并不好办，以我看，最快得再过十来天。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "现在我们难道就没法子对付那个没有用的阿吉了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "当然有。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我们只要用一个字就可以对付他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "哪个字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "拖。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我们有的是功夫。有的是钱，他们却已连吃饭都成问题，而且随时随地都得提防着我们去找他，一定也睡不着觉的，这样子拖个三五天下去，用不着我们出手，他们也要被拖垮了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "好小子，真有你的，难怪别人要叫你竹叶青。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "就算我们不去找他，他若来找我们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "一个人出来找人拼命的时候，能不能带着个受了重伤的蠢汉，和一个只会卖淫的婊子跟着他一起去？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "所以他若出来找我们，一定只有把那个苗子留下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "他可以把他们藏起来。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "城里都是我们的人，而且我又早已在他们家附近布下了眼线，他能把人藏到哪里去？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "text": "除非他们能像蚯蚓一样钻到土里去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "这次阿吉肯出来拼命，就是为了那兄妹两个，他们若是落入我们手里，阿吉还能翻得出大老板的掌心？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我们就在这里赏花喝酒，等着他们来送死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衫人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我保证不出三天，他们就会来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "text": "汤还是热的，你们快吃。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老苗子",
      "listener": "char_wa_wa",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "text": "我……我不饿。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老苗子",
      "listener": "char_wa_wa",
      "text": "我的胃口也不好，吃不下这么多，我们一人一半。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "text": "难道我不吃也不行？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老苗子",
      "listener": "char_wa_wa",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这碗汤给娃娃。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老苗子",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "不行，那是你的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_wa_wa",
      "text": "出去吃饭。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "家里有东西，你为什么要出去吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_wa_wa",
      "text": "因为我不想吃馒头。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "不想吃馒头想吃什么？是不是想吃铁头？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "我明白你的意思，这么样拖下去，连我都受不了，何况你，可是……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wa_wa",
      "speaker_name": "娃娃",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "可是你也该知道，城里都是他们的人，你又何必去送死？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_wa_wa",
      "text": "就算是去送死，也比在这里等死好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卖什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "糖炒粟子，又香又甜的糖炒粟子，二十五个大钱一斤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不贵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你想买多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一百斤。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "可是我这里一共只有十来斤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再加上你的人，就有一百斤了，我要连你的人一起买。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "我只卖栗子，不卖人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我非买不可。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "强盗，要强奸女人……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若是个女人，怎么会长胡子？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你一定是个疯子，疯子都应该被活活打死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "我……我不是，我没有疯。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若没有疯，怎么会到这里来卖糖炒栗子？这里的人穷得连饭都吃不起。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若不想被我活活打死，最好就乖乖说出是谁叫你来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你的伙伴已溜了，你还不说实话，若是被人像野狗一样打死在这里，只怕连个收尸的人都没有。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "是……是竹叶青派我来的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竹叶青是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "是大老板的军师，也是大老板面前最红的两个人之一。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有一个是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "是铁虎。他的功夫比铁头高得多，和竹叶青两个人一文一武，谁都惹不起。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "听说是到外地办事了，要过半个月才能回来。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁头呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "他有三个姨太太，三姨太最得宠，而且她一样喜欢赌，所以平时他通常都在那里。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的家住在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "大爷你问小人的家在哪里干什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问你，你就得说，人死就没有家了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "在芝麻巷。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你家里还有些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "有老婆孩子，连丫头算上，一共六个人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在就要变成八个人了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_li_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖栗子的人",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "囚为我要替你请两位客人，到你家去住两天，你若走漏了一点消息，那么我保证你的家马上就会变得只剩下一个人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只剩下那个丫头。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁大刚",
      "listener": "char_san_yi_tai",
      "text": "你要什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_yi_tai",
      "speaker_name": "三姨太",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "text": "金六银五小板凳！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁大刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个金六银五小板凳！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_yi_tai",
      "speaker_name": "三姨太",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "text": "我要的就是你这只公猴子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁大刚",
      "listener": "char_san_yi_tai",
      "text": "我要的也正是你这只母猴子，咱们倒真是天生的一对。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁大刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至尊宝，通吃！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_gang",
      "text": "吃不得！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    }
  ],
